#: ../../U/user-obsequious.rst:5
msgid "user-obsequious"
msgstr "user-obsequious"

#: ../../U/user-obsequious.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../U/user-obsequious.rst:9
msgid ""
"Emphatic form of :ref:`user-friendly`\\. Connotes a system so verbose, "
"inflexible, and determinedly simple-minded that it is nearly unusable. "
"\"Design a system any fool can use and only a fool will want to use it.\" "
"See :ref:`WIMP-environment`\\, :ref:`Macintrash`\\."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`user-friendly`\\ "
"の強調形。あまりに冗長で、融通が利かず、頑なに単純素朴で、ほとんど使い物にならないシステムを暗示する。「どんな馬鹿でも使えるシステムを設計すれば、馬鹿しか使いたがらないだろう。」\\"
" :ref:`WIMP-environment`\\ 、\\ :ref:`Macintrash`\\ を参照。"
